Title: S5 Ep. 197 Renee Davenport
Description:
Renee Davenport built her career around education. She is the VP of Sales with Age of Learning, an incredible platform that blends educational best practices, #innovative #technology, and insightful creativity to bring learning to life for children across the U.S. and around the world. Join us for our conversation to learn more about the how this company is changing what learning and education looks like.
